    "body": "Commits:\n\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/o-sumo/commit/b4f17c91e0b601a5cddbfa63ed8cb07bb863686e\">b4f17c9</a>\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/VinaNihon/commit/3b43ea75566f8d8049a4de4899f2d7367dd7a382\">3b43ea7</a>\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/VinaNihon/commit/4b1ee8efbe4b2a16de0db813971afc87c43cfccb\">4b1ee8e</a>\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/VinaNihon/commit/bc7172687bc95c5d1a0645139b3cfee232eca656\">bc71726</a>",
